<!-- SECTION 1: OVERALL SUMMARY                        -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="sec1" class="cfe-section">
    <div class="cfe-section-header">
        <span class="badge-num">1</span> Overall Summary — Ijmali Jaiza
    </div>

    <div class="highlight-box">
        <p class="tw-text-sm tw-font-semibold tw-text-slate-800 tw-m-0 tw-leading-relaxed">
            <strong>LCS (Leopards Courier Service)</strong> ek courier company hai. Is company mein couriers (delivery boys) ko unki delivery performance ke basis par
            har mahine <strong>commission/incentive</strong> diya jata hai. Yeh commission automatically calculate hoti hai — billing data, COD data,
            aur overland data alag alag databases se liya jata hai, phir saari information combine hokar ek final commission figure nikalti hai jo salary mein shamil hoti hai.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="tw-grid tw-grid-cols-1 md:tw-grid-cols-3 tw-gap-4 tw-mt-4">
        <div class="cfe-card amber">
            <div class="cfe-card-title"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt tw-mr-1"></i> Commission Period</div>
            <p class="tw-text-sm tw-text-slate-700 tw-m-0">
                Har mahine ki commission <strong>21 tarikh (pichle mahine)</strong> se shuru hokar <strong>20 tarikh (is mahine)</strong> tak ka data cover karti hai.<br><br>
                <em>Misaal: February 2026 commission = 21 Jan → 20 Feb ka data</em>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="cfe-card blue">
            <div class="cfe-card-title"><i class="fas fa-server tw-mr-1"></i> Teen Servers</div>
            <p class="tw-text-sm tw-text-slate-700 tw-m-0">
                Data teen alag servers par hai:<br>
                <strong>Server 6</strong> = Billing (Lahore)<br>
                <strong>Server 7</strong> = MIS (Lahore backup)<br>
                <strong>Server 10</strong> = Main HR / Central
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="cfe-card green">
            <div class="cfe-card-title"><i class="fas fa-rupee-sign tw-mr-1"></i> Commission Types</div>
            <p class="tw-text-sm tw-text-slate-700 tw-m-0">
                Cash Commission, COD Commission, Overland (OLE), Return COD,
                RBI (Retail Business Incentive), VAS, General Delivery — 7 qisam ki commissions
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
