        <div class="server-card server-6">
            <div class="tw-flex tw-items-center tw-gap-3 tw-mb-3">
                <div class="tw-w-10 tw-h-10 tw-bg-orange-500 tw-rounded-xl tw-flex tw-items-center tw-justify-center tw-text-white tw-font-black tw-text-lg">6</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="tw-font-black tw-text-slate-800">Server 6</div>
                    <div class="tw-text-xs tw-text-slate-500">172.16.0.6 — MySQL 5.5</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cfe-badge yellow tw-mb-2"><i class="fas fa-file-invoice-dollar"></i> Billing Server (LHR)</div>
            <p class="tw-text-xs tw-text-slate-700 tw-leading-relaxed tw-mt-2">
                <strong>Kaam:</strong> Courier deliveries ka billing data yahan rakha jata hai. Jab koi parcel deliver hota hai, uski billing detail yahan record hoti hai.<br><br>
                <strong>Aham Tables:</strong>
            </p>
            <ul class="tw-text-xs tw-text-slate-600 tw-mt-1 tw-space-y-1 tw-pl-4">
                <li><code>lcs_billing.billing_details</code> — Cash delivery records</li>
                <li><code>hr_city</code> — City + station_id mapping</li>
                <li><code>hr_employeepersonaldetail</code> — Employee basic info</li>
                <li><code>hr_employeeroutecode</code> — RouteCode ↔ EmpNo mapping</li>
                <li><code>hr_commissionpolicy</code> — Commission rate rules</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="info-box tw-mt-3 tw-text-xs">
                <strong>Important:</strong> Karachi ka Station_id yahan <code>'00592'</code> hai — yeh 3-char Code <code>'001'</code> se directly match nahi karta.
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Server 7 -->
        <div class="server-card server-7">
            <div class="tw-flex tw-items-center tw-gap-3 tw-mb-3">
                <div class="tw-w-10 tw-h-10 tw-bg-sky-500 tw-rounded-xl tw-flex tw-items-center tw-justify-center tw-text-white tw-font-black tw-text-lg">7</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="tw-font-black tw-text-slate-800">Server 7</div>
                    <div class="tw-text-xs tw-text-slate-500">172.16.0.7 — MySQL 8.0.18</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cfe-badge blue tw-mb-2"><i class="fas fa-database"></i> MIS Server (Lahore Backup)</div>
            <p class="tw-text-xs tw-text-slate-700 tw-leading-relaxed tw-mt-2">
                <strong>Kaam:</strong> Management Information System — employee location details, overland commission staging, aur RBI incentive details yahan hain.<br><br>
                <strong>Aham Tables:</strong>
            </p>
            <ul class="tw-text-xs tw-text-slate-600 tw-mt-1 tw-space-y-1 tw-pl-4">
                <li><code>hr_employeelocationdetails</code> — Employee location assignments</li>
                <li><code>hr_olecommissionprocess</code> — Overland staging data</li>
                <li><code>hr_employeeroutecode</code> — Route assignments</li>
                <li><code>hr_rbi_incentive_detail_*</code> — RBI monthly incentives</li>
                <li><code>hr_gazetted_holidays</code> — Public holidays</li>
                <li><code>lcs_billing_download.billing_details</code> — MIS billing download</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="info-box tw-mt-3 tw-text-xs">
                <strong>Location:</strong> Agar employee ka location Server 7 par update nahi, to us employee ki commission process nahi hogi. MIS team se coordinate karo.
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Server 10 -->
        <div class="server-card server-10">
            <div class="tw-flex tw-items-center tw-gap-3 tw-mb-3">
                <div class="tw-w-10 tw-h-10 tw-bg-purple-600 tw-rounded-xl tw-flex tw-items-center tw-justify-center tw-text-white tw-font-black tw-text-lg">10</div>
                <div>
                    <div class="tw-font-black tw-text-slate-800">Server 10</div>
                    <div class="tw-text-xs tw-text-slate-500">172.16.0.10 — MySQL 8.0.27</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cfe-badge purple tw-mb-2"><i class="fas fa-crown"></i> Main HR / Central (18th Floor)</div>
