        <div class="tw-flex tw-flex-col tw-gap-3">
            <div class="cfe-card amber">
                <div class="cfe-card-title">Step 5 (Master) mein kya hota hai?</div>
                <ul class="tw-text-sm tw-text-slate-700 tw-space-y-1.5 tw-pl-4 tw-m-0">
                    <li>Duplicate check — agar already process hua hai to error</li>
                    <li>Puraane records delete karo us month ke</li>
                    <li>Cash, COD, OLE, Return COD sab ke records uthao</li>
                    <li>Employee eligibility check karo (<code>hr_empcommissioneligibility</code>)</li>
                    <li>Attendance se working days calculate karo</li>
                    <li>Zone logic apply karo (Local / Same Zone / Other Zone)</li>
                    <li>Rate table (<code>hr_commissionpolicy</code>) se rate lao</li>
